These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, russian, mexican
1. the mexican is on the left of the russian##1
2. the mexican is between the brazilian and the russian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | mexican | russian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, mystery, adventure
1. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching mystery movies and the person watching adventure movies##2
2. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | spy | mystery |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, house, salsa
1. the fan of house is between the fan of r&b and the fan of salsa##2
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | house | r&b |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: horse, goldfish, hamster
1. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
2. the owner of the hamster is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the horse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | horse | hamster | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, sprite, iced-tea
1. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking sprite##2
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | sprite | tea | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
